title: WikileakS.org mirror archive (Feb 10th 2008)
description:
Archive Dated: February 10th, 2008


Wikileaks.org, a clearinghouse of whistleblower documents was taken down by a California Court Injunction. 

Torrent files contain a dated Wikileaks.org archive. This is a snapshot of the documents and may soon be out of date. For more info, checkout the blog: wikileak.org

Archive received from www.cryptome.org
